dc_title_s: Height Modernization (ILHMP) LiDAR Data [Winnebago County, Illinois] (2007)
dc_creator_sm: This data set was developed for the United States Geological Survey by Sanborn Mapping.
dc_description_s: Provide FEMA compliant elevation, topography and contour map of Winnebago County, Illinois. Provide Bare Earth DEM (vegetation removal) of Winnebago County, Illinois.
